{"tid":700916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美再揮關稅大棒時　京推擴大進口「組合拳」　另14號蓬佩奧受王毅邀請訪華","createTime":"2018-06-13T17:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T23:20:50.000Z","uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3748106481f6c08d5ea7ea27f06f82c752a7ab3","tid":700916,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2094149/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2094149%2F&d=2NGsKzeN1o0%2FOZGYyGosMvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=693bdce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2094149/</a><br />\n<br />\n美再揮關稅大棒時 京推擴大進口「組合拳」<br />\n<br />\n美國政府即將公布新一波對華關係措施之際，國務院常務會議今天確定進一步擴大進口，增加進口關係民生的日用消費品等。會議重申維護自由貿易。<br />\n<br />\n會議指出，為推進互利共贏開放戰略、維護自由貿易，在穩定出口的同時，要進一步擴大進口，倒逼國內產業改造提升，更好滿足群眾多樣化需求。"},{"pid":"70aa1099434b417c76bf933998fba726e0e0cff5","tid":700916,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:29:45.000Z","msg":"會議確定，為適應消費升級和供給提質需要，支持關係民生的日用消費品、醫藥和康復、養老護理等設備進口，落實降低部分商品進口稅率措施，減少中間流通環節，清理不合理加價，讓群眾切實感受到降稅帶來的好處。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>加大進口民生日用消費品</strong><br />\n<br />\n會議又提出，發展服務貿易，促進研發設計、物流、諮詢服務、節能環保等生產性服務進口；完善免稅店政策，擴大免稅品進口。增加有助於轉型發展的技術裝備進口。<br />\n<br />\n會議要求，要優化進口通關流程，開展海關「經認證的經營者（AEO）」國際互認．清理進口環節不合理管理措施和收費。<br />\n<br />\n在創新進口貿易方式方面，會議表示，支持跨境電商等新業態發展，加強外貿誠信體系建設和知識產權保護。促進對外貿易和對外投資有效互動。"},{"pid":"6f42030674f1b98f52fd5f189c9f670bce5ac055","tid":700916,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1401426-20180613.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1401426-20180613.htm&d=2NGsKzeN1o0%2FOZGYyGosMvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=b79fa199\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1401426-20180613.htm&h=f59b4237\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1401426-20180613.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧明天訪華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1401426_1_L_20180613105755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1401426_1_L_20180613105755.jpg&h=7a8c65e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽宣布，應國務委員兼外交部長王毅的邀請，美國國務卿蓬佩奧將於明天訪華，中美將就兩國關係發展，以及共同關心的重要國際和地區問題交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n外交部表示，王毅與蓬佩奧明天下午將會一同會見記者。"},{"pid":"a2418bf6f210ab85b3c53bd356e2ea90d7d54ca8","tid":700916,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"咁叫亮劍定亮白旗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c397828e94b13daa01bf58ac1dd7e5e89d15f8","tid":700916,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"4bb4b47f9c357abadbfbe6b3396c3c7675961c85","tid":700916,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2418bf6f210ab85b3c53bd356e2ea90d7d54ca8","tid":700916,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"咁叫亮劍定亮白旗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:39:58.000Z","msg":"上得連登多，而家玩「組合拳」<img src=\"https://lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之但求美國唔徵收關稅就當嬴"},{"pid":"36d21d93bc24f38379ef3920af81422789f3f068","tid":700916,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T21:50:19.000Z","msg":"降左部分關稅，整體仍然好高<br />\n<br />\n美國唔好中計，偷技術用先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf826c8ffde73a9c51b2e757b76b2d356d039cc3","tid":700916,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2418bf6f210ab85b3c53bd356e2ea90d7d54ca8","tid":700916,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"咁叫亮劍定亮白旗？<img src=\"/assets/face